{"type":"message","id":"2a0a5935","parentId":"225f277d","timestamp":"2026-03-30T00:02:50.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Organizing final message**\n\nI need to prepare a plain text message that highlights the WhatsApp number. It's important to note that I've coordinated Ares to read through all tasks, and there shouldn’t be any backlog or next items without a clear owner. This helps ensure everything is organized and accounted for, making it easier to manage tasks going forward. I want to be thorough so that nothing gets overlooked!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_06e3a5da87e674290169c9bda7312c81918a0a7ee9d2361c84\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpyb2plBJ-eSKVNxK6tAD1xEqkONDnGCkCdL5T2q1XkzZYuRkmMU_Qdr5b9E3yd7ZeLZ4apYx4H0qGzlnEbf44mogfxNiyC1PYWg9WgQfiXV5mKSj-Jn5e6sKNjPMBcTJO7kjAYhZnuFXEoBPC83Dkx9IuOuzNnkeQPIElHTpdFUnd4CrmlG8jZgL_jp-Jv8-gd9QMRVVituB6NsQotB51p69HkcSEhOSrRFz7RlV7RYiX-m23EQibWVNHUcNZ1sSScw4J4-skDkoL6igRFCDiRqifYWbzfd_4alQEteWMCKZwI8qZ_muL01GVV8KMBWf9l94ESP-DZ4gbGNVTXriTUcMYEsGmMoBeVzo_uIger3ExmLWem712vyforZXUsnaEsOVxnBuPTjmdS89Hx3Vf010WOptSDtCYLqAQSUZZDTdguoRR1sXHyRudlTat3mO4kcN0wVD8Q1j8fZdaqrIDma29Vap_EiPw5HkSpLUE8LDUJTR0QsXdfOer-cGfnU3vw-FMVdYPON5Oj5DTXCw4suBfbpQKKJOvnrbTkuXc0lJyJ2b_S6HualdQCRTjh7bdDsb1aavb4ijwIjpWfcZiDyarEOIZrf0YUpTAJQ2PGMyoaIEe4sMK-ey_Jln_AFvVHAH-Vtv_1ymgAKWF5V1soQ-PhKHsHbdi4CnQeWvts92BjREZvbPOzPlxzfeePci1a5DXQiGfxL1UZY3XJREJOboA_SZAWkm424bfPStXgs9xTgwiPb1FGme6Tqmw3jgyL8JdJGpMbLD7LeCu46pcV-e_TYsMOpF6rurJ_jhB6KYaa0piMXBJoZiEzDveKe9pv254Xdbz5EdVb9OI0dYi_wRqZv66zVv0nRIueVEI_i9VsjOeTWCmNsNf2xfRjMBmZVeXX8H9IdjAVSP8do4_2mPGH2Tbun7JIe7ZoHq1ul6MXaPzgO9AGwVR23AwgtLdpqtPFpHUqv2EdBI0nxYoTeamCh3cB4yp6ssO1Su5hPZ9czkfY9sgRWMZXk429Zkm8LNySigmeA1pWf9xE-f7KGUydQ==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Organizing final message**\\n\\nI need to prepare a plain text message that highlights the WhatsApp number. It's important to note that I've coordinated Ares to read through all tasks, and there shouldn’t be any backlog or next items without a clear owner. This helps ensure everything is organized and accounted for, making it easier to manage tasks going forward. I want to be thorough so that nothing gets overlooked!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"Revisé completo el Tasks Tracker.\n\nMoví/coordiné:\n- Coordiné activamente con Ares la tarea **“Definir sesión de entrenamiento siguiente”**.\n- Ares dejó definición operativa clara:\n  - decisión: **mantener Next**\n  - contenido: la siguiente sesión sigue siendo **Pierna A**\n  - primer paso: **preparar y enviar la rutina concreta al grupo Smart Project**\n  - bloqueo explícito: **no hay confirmación verificable de envío real al canal externo**\n- Actualicé la nota de esa tarea en Notion con esa coordinación y mantuve el estado en **Next**.\n\nQué quedó bloqueado / esperando:\n- **“Definir sesión de entrenamiento siguiente”** sigue en **Next** hasta ver evidencia real de envío.\n- No encontré otras tareas en **Backlog** o **Next** con dueño claro que requirieran coordinación activa en esta ronda.\n- La tarea en **Backlog** sin owner claro (**“Recuérdame que no te he respondido…”**) se queda igual por falta de responsable asignado.\n\nQué sigue:\n- Hacer seguimiento a Ares hasta obtener una de estas dos cosas:\n  1) evidencia real de envío al grupo Smart Project, o\n  2) bloqueo nuevo y explícito que impida ese envío.\n\nMensaje externo pendiente:\n- Enviar este resumen por **WhatsApp al +573183718246**.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06e3a5da87e674290169c9bda99a348191a6c5a19a241f8a5f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1663,"output":337,"cacheRead":29568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31568,"cost":{"input":0.004157500000000001,"output":0.0050550000000000005,"cacheRead":0.007391999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0166045}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774828961810,"responseId":"resp_06e3a5da87e674290169c9bda5d6f08191a10941c27a9086ee"}}
